                    "company": "HBB Groep",
                    "description": "HBB Groep is a dynamic organization that develops and realizes construction projects with a professional and committed team. By linking your vision and ideas with our expertise, we are able to offer you an in-depth and well-thought-out accommodation solution. With more then 75 years of experience, our team constantly works towards the future.\n\nThanks to our long-term vision, we can invest in durable and lasting business relations with our partners and clients. In addition to cooperation with the government, semi-public organizations, housing corporations, investors and partners, HBB Groep also invests actively in competitions, tenders, turnkey constructions and construction teams. We closely monitor all steps in the process, giving our partners guaranteed professionalism and reliability throughout every phase of the project.\n\nA sustainable cooperation with mutual respect is the key to success. A large number of companies have already discovered how reliable a partnership with HBB Groep is. And it is only by working with a likeminded party such as HBB Groep that a partnership can truly achieve its full potential. We work with an extensive variety of partners, from governments to independent property owners and other market parties. Our meticulously documented procedures and agreements provide a solid basis for successful partnerships.\nwww.hbbgroep.nl",
